2026-01-30 06:55 ET - News Release
TORONTO, Jan.  30, 2026  (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) --
Alamos Gold Inc.
(
TSX:AGI; NYSE:AGI
) (“Alamos” or the “Company”) today reported new results from its underground exploration program at the Young-Davidson mine. Underground exploration drilling from both the mid and lower mine extended higher-grade gold mineralization within multiple zones in the hanging wall of the Young-Davidson deposit. In addition, expansion drilling within the Young-Davidson syenite continues to extend gold mineralization beyond Mineral Reserves and Mineral Resources.
South Syenite Zone: high-grade gold mineralization intersected within a syenite intrusion located in the hanging wall, 285 metres (“m”) south of the Northgate Shaft in an area that has seen limited historical drilling.
